 73â†’/**
 74â†’ * Returns a flow that contains first elements satisfying the given [predicate].
 75â†’ *
 76â†’ * Note, that the resulting flow does not contain the element on which the [predicate] returned `false`.
 77â†’ * See [transformWhile] for a more flexible operator.
