 95â†’ * The receiver of the `transformWhile` is [FlowCollector] and thus `transformWhile` is a
 96â†’ * flexible function that may transform emitted element, skip it or emit it multiple times.
 97â†’ *
 98â†’ * This operator generalizes [takeWhile] and can be used as a building block for other operators.
 99â†’ * For example, a flow of download progress messages can be completed when the
100â†’ * download is done but emit this last message (unlike `takeWhile`):
